1. Moj *veš* se suši na terasi. (My laundry is drying on the terrace.)
2. Da li si oprao taj *veš* koji si ostavio u mašini? (Did you wash the laundry that you left in the washing machine?)
3. Moram da kupim nov *veš* za plažu. (I need to buy new swimwear for the beach.)
4. Izvini što sam ti zamazao taj *veš*, kupiću ti novi. (Sorry for staining your clothes, I'll buy you new ones.)
5. Naša prodavnica prodaje različite vrste *veša*. (Our store sells different types of underwear.)
6. Sutra ću da peglam *veš* čitav dan. (Tomorrow I'll be ironing clothes all day.)
7. *Veš* je našao svoje mesto u ormanu. (The laundry found its place in the closet.)
8. Ne volim kada mi se *veš* skuplja na jednom mestu. (I don't like when my laundry piles up in one place.)
9. Ovaj *veš* se ne sme prati na visokim temperaturama. (This laundry should not be washed at high temperatures.)
10. Moraćemo da kupimo novu *veš* mašinu, ova više ne radi dobro. (We'll have to buy a new washing machine, this one isn't working properly anymore.)